  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430660/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.poster.avif?t=1726814842\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430660/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.webm?t=1726814842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430660/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.mp4?t=1726814842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>MiceGard is an adventure game where you'll play as mouse-vikings. Immerse yourself in a unique world inspired by Scandinavian mythology.<br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Epic saga of trust, betrayal, bravery and cute little animals.<br></li><li> Short story of furry Norse heroes.<br></li><li> One-evening experience of heroism and mystery!<br></li><li> Capricious Gods and eldritch magic.<br></li><li> Choose wisely for even mouse's choice matters!<br></li><li> Furious battles and cunning tactical challenges.<br></li><li> Protect your village and kin - but watch out for dark conspiracies!<br></li><li> Become the hero people want you to be - even if it is mice-people.<br></li><li> Enjoy art created with love for mice and norse myths.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430660/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.poster.avif?t=1726814842\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430660/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.webm?t=1726814842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430660/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.mp4?t=1726814842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>MiceGard is an adventure game where you'll play as mouse-vikings. Immerse yourself in a unique world inspired by Scandinavian mythology.<br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Epic saga of trust, betrayal, bravery and cute little animals.<br></li><li> Short story of furry Norse heroes.<br></li><li> One-evening experience of heroism and mystery!<br></li><li> Capricious Gods and eldritch magic.<br></li><li> Choose wisely for even mouse's choice matters!<br></li><li> Furious battles and cunning tactical challenges.<br></li><li> Protect your village and kin - but watch out for dark conspiracies!<br></li><li> Become the hero people want you to be - even if it is mice-people.<br></li><li> Enjoy art created with love for mice and norse myths.</li></ul>",
